column3: salmon is great..Waygu beef is great
column4: but just the source is a bit not that great...it's more like A one source which I never liked...duck is okay..last but not least is the fried milk. It's great but it can be better if the shell is not that thick
column5: I was expecting something more crispy and thin instead of a "nutshell"...but inside is warm and tasty milky cream...yumyum! Overall good place for dating
column6: small portion you can eat without losing style.
